info.author: Martijn Jasperse
info.description: The module provides a simple way to store and recall pandas timeseries data from a database. It provides greater control and flexibility than pandas.io.sql, while being easier to use as it automatically converts the timeseries index timestamps into SQL-compatible strings.
info.name: timesquirrel
info.summary: A simple interface between timeseries data and SQLite3 databases
info.html_description: The module provides a simple way to store and recall pandas timeseries data from a database. It provides greater control and flexibility than pandas.io.sql, while being easier to use as it automatically converts the timeseries index timestamps into SQL-compatible strings.
